    <h1 itemprop="headline" class="title">Inside the Impossible Dream of the Nuclear-Powered 1958 Ford Nucleon</h1>
  

  

  
    <h2 class="dek">Driving more than 5,000 miles without stopping to refuel sounds like a &#039;50s fever dream&mdash;because it was.</h2>
  

  <div class="article-metadata">
    
      By
      
        <a href="/author/james-gilboy" data-analytics="Author James Gilboy">James Gilboy</a>
      
    
    
